.name
VChess
.fullname
Vector-Chess
.type
Thinking Game
.short
Excellent, easys to use chess game
.description
A powerfull fully functional (non crippled) shareware chess game
written in Amiga Oberon. The program has a lot of
features, is easy to use and don't needs much memory (only 500K).
There are many new features, Opening-library is fully rewritten.
I think, that playing-strength is big enough for average players.
